===Pronunciation===
*πάλαι / palai / pal'-ahee
*Probably another form for [[πάλιν]] {{GG|3825}} (through the idea of retrocession); (adverbially) formerly, or (relatively) sometime since; (elliptically as adjective) ancient: 
